The Hawks have arrested former EP rugby president Cheeky Watson‚ along with Nadia Gerwel‚ Andrea Wessels and Mandisa Mkaza on charges of fraud or corruption. It is believed to be linked to the Nelson Mandela Bay municipality’s Integrated Public Transport System’s (IPTS’s) funds of R200m. They were due to appear in the Port Elizabeth Magistrate’s Court on Friday morning. TMG Digital/The Herald